{"tid":1852995,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎｜買唔到發爛渣】阿伯買唔到口罩推跌貨品 正義男怒插：你問民建聯攞啦","createTime":"2020-01-30T17:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T17:15:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d0e394035fd91e0b07b71641261761ec563be96","tid":1852995,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_722140_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_722140_0&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA5a0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=fd67853b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_722140_0&h=24fcbae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_722140_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎｜買唔到發爛渣】阿伯買唔到口罩推跌貨品 正義男怒插：你問民建聯攞啦<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/video/20200130/480pix/1580367922_d3e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fvideo%2F20200130%2F480pix%2F1580367922_d3e1.jpg&h=4bfce61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳片段，懷疑有老漢因購買口罩不果，大發雷霆喪鬧店員，又將貨品推跌，引發一名男子挺身而出怒插。<br />\n<br />\n男子的說話內容顯示，有老漢因排隊搶購口罩失敗，怪罪於年輕店員，又掃跌貨架上的貨品，屈臣氏門外的貨物散落一地。該正義男不滿阿伯發難：「你去問蔣麗芸、民建聯攞（口罩）！我夠想要口罩！你估X兩句就有？」正義男挺身而出的畫面被市民拍下，惹網民熱議，不少網民大撐正義男「鬧得好」。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【壹週刊直播平台 ChannelNEXT】<br />\n<br />\n立即睇<br />\n<br />\n全城抗暴 區區論壇同你深度剖析<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"60eb7bd86ca04bd9cd2158d2e7c736f55b1d6d65","tid":1852995,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"親共禮義廉依家真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}